summary: Just something I drew for fun, may or may not actually happen. But this is Celestia with the Scorn symbiote. I considered...
caption:
Just something I drew for fun, may or may not actually happen. But this is Celestia with the Scorn symbiote. I considered drawing her mane and tail but decided against it, I like how Scorn seems to have a very sleek appearance so yeah

Since Celestia is like. Probably THE most powerful alicorn alive and symbiotes enhance their host’s strength even further, Celescorn here is probably the most overpowered creature in existence. What’ll she do with herself?? probably drink tea and beat the shit out of bad guys before locking them in Tartarus forever

Enjoy

title: Ami Pascal è fiduciosa che l'accordo Marvel & Sony continuerà
body:
Ami Pascal è fiduciosa che l’accordo Marvel & Sony continuerà

La produttrice in franchising di Spider-Man, Amy Pascal, ha rivelato che spera che l’accordo tra Sony e Marvel proseguirà durante un’intervista con Vanity Fair.

Mentre l’inclusione di Spider-Man nell’UCM ha dimostrato di avere successo sia per Marvel Studios che per Sony, il successo al botteghino di quest’ultimo studio con Venom ha fatto nascere voci secondo cui l’azienda avrebbe optato per…
